 3. the security-guard is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the designer is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
