 3. the brazilian is on the far right##1
 4. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
