.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, weightlifting, badminton, surfing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, indie, rock, techno, trance
5 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, rabbit, turtle
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller, ship, tram
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the fan of rock is the person who's sport is surfing##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Sport      | weightlifting | surfing    | water-polo   | badminton   | soccer |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | rock   | trance | techno | indie  |
| Pet           | fish     | rabbit | goat   | turtle | bird   |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | tram   | car    | ship   | roller |

